# Kirana Hub — Environment Setup

## ⚠️ This file is NOT included in GitHub for security reasons.
## Create a `.env.local` file in the project root with these variables:

```env
MONGODB_URI=mongodb+srv://<user>:<password>@<cluster>.mongodb.net/kirana_hub?retryWrites=true&w=majority
JWT_SECRET=your_strong_random_secret_key_here
NODE_ENV=development
```

## Getting your MongoDB URI:
1. Go to [MongoDB Atlas](https://cloud.mongodb.com)
2. Click Connect → Drivers
3. Copy the connection string
4. Replace `<password>` with your DB user password
